#**SteemNova About Us**
     
 
**SteemNova** founded by @mys is the first Open Source/online Massive Multiplayer Online Strategy Game (MMOSG) built on the Steem Blockchain. **SteemNova** was created with a simple mission of delivering the best and satisfactory gaming experience to our gamers under a safe and enjoyable atmosphere. At **SteemNova**, our gamers come first and are dear to us that why we offer a 24/7 service. **SteemNova** is fair and results are highly accurate. We run a transparent service here at **SteemNova** which ensures that there is no cause for alarm. 

We make it hard for gamers to run out of options as you can build up alliances with other **SteemNova** gamers. **SteemNova** provides you with the privacy and comfort derived from playing our games from your home as well as the opportunity to build up your IQ, learn how to work in a team and learn to develop strategies. 

We do not ask for any sign up fee, you gain access to our games free. 

We pay our winnings as fast as possible without delay making SteemNova a trusted platform. We do not ask our gamers for their billing information. We respect our gamers privacy by asking them to provide minimal information.


**@steemnova** is the official Steem account of the game - **#steemnova** is preferred SteemNova community tag at Steemit.com



**SteemNova Unique Feature List**: 


- Massively Multiplayer Online Strategy Game (MMOSG) Space Browser game 
- "Ogame Retro"-based rules and mechanics (Open Source Browsergame Framework "2Moons" fork) 
- No Game-Operators, no rules, no bans - For Steemians (SteemConnect authentication) 
- Competition between TOP 8 Alliances for Steem cryptocurrency reward 
- Free-to-play, win-to-pay - Biggest "Ogame Retro"-clone server as of 2018.



**For questions, concerns, doubts and suggestions, you can contact us on discord https://discord.gg/dTXWMSS or on GitHub @https://github.com/steemnova/steemnova**
